Nearly any one can obtain a driver's license.  Nearly any one can later abuse that privledge by speeding, drinking while imparied, etc.  Nearly any one can also drive just fine once that license is expired or revoked, people do it all the time, in some cases for years before they are ever caught.  A license is nothing more than a means for the state or government that isues it to raise revenue, and a form of identification.  <br>
