I once made the statement that liberal pussies were ruining this country with all the special interests.  It was those very same liberal pussy special interest groups that caused the laws to become less strict, then allowed for appeal after appeal after appeal for a conviction, and finally let people like this simply serve jail time rather then be executed.  People for the most part no longer fear the consequences of their own actions.  <br>
<br>
You really want to see people change, make the law something to be feared and respected.  In all but a few cases these days the DNA evidence is enough for a 100% judgement of guilt.  In this case they know for a fact that this woman selfishly ignored her own child to do something she freely elected to do.  The moment the court ruled her as guilty she should have been executed.  <br>
<br>
Until we as a nation stop with the total pussification that allows us to say things like &quot;she was addicted&quot; as if that were a fucking excuse then people like this bitch will continue to kill or harm innocent people.<br>
<br>
There is no excuse for what happened here, none other than the ones our society continue to make.  Point in case, it is well documented that convicted child molesters do not &quot;rehab&quot;.  All the registrations in the world do not stop repeat offenders yet we as a society continue to let these animals out of jail ,and then to live among us so that they can once again commit their horrible atrosities.<br>
<br>
I say fuck that, one conviction for a crime of this nature should earn you swift death.  You've already proven you have no qualms about preying upon young children (many of whom grow up with all manner of mental and emotional issues of their own as a result of this shit) what more fucking excuses do we need to make to justify letting these scum continue to live?<br>
<br>
We as a society allow the conditions to exist that perpetuate the continued horrifying acts we see people do to children on a daily basis.  It is up to us to change it, no one else will.<br>
